name: VMWARE VSPHERE 8.X - Content Pack
summary: Content pack containing Dashboards and parsed security events only
description:
- Dashboard 1: VCenter Dashboard with VCenter Events, SSO Activites, Virtual Machines activities

- Dashboard 2: VCSA Dashboards with all the tabs associated to one application_name (field created automatically thanks to syslog)

- Pipeline filtering VCenter events

- Pipelines parsing security events (authentication, admin action, virtual machine activities (knowing which users did the speicifed action on the VM)

source.@value:
pipeline "VCENTER - ssoadminserver"
stage 0 match pass
rule "Syslog - VMWARE ESXI - ssoadminserver 01"
stage 1 match pass
rule "Syslog - VMWARE ESXI - ssoadminserver 02"
stage 2 match pass
rule "VMWARE ssoadminserver - vmw_vc_return_value replace carriage return"
stage 3 match pass
rule "VMWARE vmw_vc_ssoadminserver_action"
end

title.@value: Syslog - VMWARE VCSA - extract vmw_vc_domain from vmw_vc_user

source.@value:
pipeline "VCENTER - vpxd-main - vpxLRO"
stage 0 match either
rule "Syslog - VMWARE ESXI - vpxd-main - VPXLRO 1"
stage 1 match either
rule "Syslog - VMWARE ESXI - vpxd-main - VPXLRO 2"
end

pipeline "VCenter - vpxd-main"
stage 0 match either
rule "VMWARE Replace carriage return"
stage 1 match either
rule "Syslog - VMWARE ESXI - vpxd-main"
stage 2 match either
rule "Syslog - VMWARE ESXI - vpxd-main 02"
end

title.@value: VMWARE ssoadminserver - vmw_vc_return_value replace carriage return

source.@value:
rule "VMWARE ssoadminserver - vmw_vc_return_value replace carriage return"

when 
    has_field("vmw_vc_return_value") AND regex("Vmodl method", to_string($message.vmw_vc_desc)).matches == true
then
    let carr_message = regex_replace("\\\\n", to_string($message."vmw_vc_return_value"),"",true);

    set_field ("vmw_vc_return_value", carr_message);
end

rule "VMWARE Replace carriage return"

when 
    has_field("message")
then
    let rep_message = regex_replace("\\\\n-->", to_string($message."message"),"",true);

    set_field ("message", rep_message);
end
